NUMBER 593
NAME Temple of Amilor Library
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
A group of young acolytes, sitting on the chairs encircling the tables which
fill the center of this quiet study, listen to an old priest recounting an
ancient battle against the Sharkhor and their allies. Tall oak bookcases
line the walls, crammed with a variety of worn volumes. Within a stone
fireplace, merrily blazing flames fill the room with warmth and the scent
of spiced cider brewing in an iron pot. Across the room is a huge glass bowl
containing many colorful fish.
*DESCRIPTION_END
