It is a wonderful impressionistic portrait of Amilor and Shemri standing hand
in hand over the world.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 3
Myriad varieties of fish swim lazily through the clear blue water contained
within this bowl.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 7
The shelves are filled with tomes on history and mythology as well as a few
works of fiction.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB PUSH 7
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You take a treatise on the Faith of Amilor down from the bookcase and pore through it a while before putting it, carefully, back in its place.
    ECHO OTHERS %N removes a tome from the bookcase and studies it for a while before putting it back on the shelf.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PULL 7
  CLEARVERB
