NUMBER 592
NAME Temple of Amilor Courtyard
DAY_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
As you step into the large enclosed courtyard in the heart of the temple,
you see an immense block of purest white marble, placed exactly in the
center of the area, covered with images of sea creatures playing in the
waves or battling sharks. Shimmering runes decorate the sides of the
sculpture, formed from deep cuts filled with molten silver. Placed
before the altar is a large golden basin encrusted with glittering
sapphires, pearls and aquamarines. Each of the four walls has been painted
with a mural depicting a season of the year and waters effect on it.
Rising from the floor, behind the altar, is a golden oak of majestic
strength and beauty.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 944 ADJ1=294 ADJ2=355 VAL2=591
ITEM 1 236 ADJ1=347 ADJ2=187
ITEM 2 554 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=468
ITEM 3 229 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=468
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
This large golden bowl has been formed into the shape of an open clamshell.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 3
The tree shimmers with a golden hue the color of sunlight, almost as if
it captures beams from the day's light and retains their warmth within
its mighty trunk. The roots of the oak extend gently around the altar
cradling it almost protectively. As you stand, transfixed by the nearly
overpowering beauty of the tree you hear a soothing female voice over the
soft rustling of the tree's branches... "For my husband and his children,
a gift of love from my heart..."
*DESCRIPTION_END
 IFVERB TOUCH 1
 IFVAR ALIGN => 50
 IFVAR GEN = 0
   ECHO PLAYER You are filled with a deep sense of peace and calm as Amilor's voice sounds within your mind, "Take heart my son, I am ever with you."
   ECHO OTHERS The runes on the altar glow with a light of their own as %N opens %h soul to Amilor.
 ENDIF
  IFVAR GEN = 1
   ECHO PLAYER You are filled with a deep sense of peace and calm as Amilor's voice sounds within your mind, "Take heart my daughter, I am ever with you."
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
   IFVAR ALIGN => 10
   IFVAR ALIGN =< 49
     ECHO PLAYER You feel at peace as Amilor's voice fills your thoughts, "Seek to find the truth in your heart child, and you will find me."
     ECHO OTHERS The runes on the altar glow with a light of their own as %N opens %h soul to Amilor.
   ENDIF
   ENDIF
      IFVAR ALIGN => 1
      IFVAR ALIGN =< 9
	ECHO PLAYER A sense of calm washes over you as Amilor's voice speaks in your mind, "My child, you are well on the path to understanding. First seek the Truth inside, know the darkness you face for what it is, then will you come to know me.
	ECHO OTHERS The runes on the altar glow with a light of their own as %N opens %h soul to Amilor.
      ENDIF
      ENDIF
	IFVAR ALIGN =< 0
	IFVAR ALIGN => -5
	  ECHO PLAYER A deep power radiates from the altar as a voice speaks within you, "Child, if you wish to find the peace of my Realm, you must seek for the truth Inside, confront the face of darkness unfraid and open your heart to others.
	  ECHO OTHERS The runes on the altar glow deeply as %N stands transfixed in their light as %s is judged by Amilor.
	ENDIF
	ENDIF
	  IFVAR ALIGN =< -6
	  IFVAR ALIGN => -99
	    ECHO ALL The runes on the altar flash an angry red as a tongue of lightning lashes out and bathes %N in flame.
	    DAMAGE ELECTRIC 5 Electricity crackles around %N!
	  ENDIF
	  ENDIF
	    IFVAR ALIGN =< -100
	      ECHO ALL The runes on the altar glow a deep purple and the heavens rumble violently as a single shaft of lightning streaks downward and strikes %N.
       ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Father,_grant_me_passage!
	IFVAR INTNUM3 = 56
		IFITEM 4
			ECHO PLAYER The stairway already exists.
		ENDIF
		IFNOITEM 4
			ECHO ALL A shimmering blue stairway, fashioned from the lapping waters of Amilor's domain comes into existence before you, arching upwards towards a chamber above the temple.
			NEWITEM 4 81 ADJ1=287 ADJ2=29
		ENDIF
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER A voice fills your mind, "Only my High Priestess may call upon me for this."
