IFPREVERB CLIMB 4
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = 56
     ECHO PLAYER You climb the stairway into the vestry. As you step off of the last step the stairway shimmers gently and disappears behind you.
     ECHO OTHERS %P climbs the stairway. As %n moves from the last step the stairway shimmers slightly and disappears.
     MOVEGROUP 1036
     REMOVEITEM 4
    ELSE
     ECHO PLAYER As you step onto the stairway it quickly dissipates, causing you to fall to the floor ungracefully.
