NUMBER 43
NAME Temple of Amilor Knights' Lounge
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
Comfortable chairs and couches are carefully arranged around the
interior of a room whose walls reflect the beliefs and attitudes of
its inhabitants. Weapons and shields have been carefully placed upon
the walls to seamlessly integrate with artful mosaics and paintings
of Amilor's Knights engaged in the tasks of conquering His enemies.
*DESCRIPTION_END
