ITEM 1 401 ADJ1=178
EXTEND 1 of Amilor
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The polished marble has been artfully carved to give the illusion of
waves continously moving over the face of the arch.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Sculpted from a strange transparent stone through which can be seen the
shimmering blue waters of Amilor's domain, constantly moving in harmonious
symphony. Glittering magics play around, and throughout, the entire
form of the statue, being most prevalent around the outstretched arms
which seem to offer comfort and blessing.
*DESCRIPTION_END
