NUMBER 1039
NAME Temple of Amilor Hidden Shelter
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
Scattered about are numerous crates, barrels and racks containing food,
supplies and weapons, providing a last sanctuary in times of great peril.
The pool you just emerged from appears to be filled by a branch of a
swift subterranean river, providing a source of fresh cool water before
it exits through an opening in the wall. Cots fill up the empty spaces,
the only other furnishing is a framed portrait of Amilor gazing out over
a shattered and dead wasteland. A lever juts from one wall next to a small
peephole.
*DESCRIPTION_END
