ITEM 1 236 ADJ1=534
ITEM 2 60 ADJ1=395
ITEM 3 1457
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The gleaming walls shimmer with the colors of the ocean, the patterns shifting
and swirling as you gaze about the room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The pure white coral which forms the altar has been intricately carved with
a delicate lace-like pattern, highlighted by the burning candles placed
within it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
Each piece of pale pink- and rose-colored coral resembles a flower in full
bloom, the ruffled edges adding to the illusion. Interwoven between them are
satin ribbons in pastel shades of pink, blue, white and rose.
*DESCRIPTION_END
