NUMBER 1036
NAME Temple of Amilor High Priestess's Vestry
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
This comfortable chamber serves as a private meeting area and retreat for
the high priestess. High atop the temple, the large windows grant breath-
taking views of the shimmering silver waves of the Inner Sea and the
snow-capped peaks of Shartan's Fangs. The lush green forests and farmlands
surrounding the city add to the sense of peace that you find prevalent
within this temple. The southern half of this room is dominated by a large
circular table, crafted from ocean-cooled basalt which has been smoothed to a
mirror smooth surface and surrounded by velvet covered chairs. Across the
chamber are soft lounges and a cozy fireplace for less formal meetings.
Various works of art depict scenes from Amilor's realms.
*DESCRIPTION_END
